headline: KEYCORP LOWERS ITS PRIME LENDING RATE TO 7.25 PERCENT
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE: KEY) and its banking affiliates have lowered their prime lending rate to 7.25 percent from 7.50 percent, effective tomorrow, Sept. 18, 2025.
